summary: This document is a U.S. Customs and Border Protection (CBP) automated notification email indicating that a 'Person Lookout Query' was performed on Ghislaine Maxwell on October 21, 2019, at the San Ysidro land border crossing. It shows law enforcement was actively checking her records.

keyFacts: A law enforcement query was run on Ghislaine Maxwell on October 21, 2019.
The query was a 'Person Lookout Query' performed by U.S. Customs and Border Protection (CBP).
The query was accessed from the San Ysidro land border crossing location.
The document indicates active law enforcement interest in Maxwell's movements in late 2019.
